          { "type": "button", "text": { "type": "plain_text", "text": "View full report" }, "value": "view::pigment::run_2026w18", "action_id": "view_full_report", "url": "https://www.notion.so/competitive-intel/run_2026w18" },
          { "type": "button", "text": { "type": "plain_text", "text": "Mark as read" }, "value": "ack::pigment::run_2026w18", "action_id": "mark_as_read" },
          { "type": "button", "style": "danger", "text": { "type": "plain_text", "text": "Flag" }, "value": "flag::pigment::run_2026w18", "action_id": "flag_signal" }
        ]
      },
      { "type": "divider" },
      {
        "type": "section",
        "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*🟡 MEDIUM — Planful*  `NEW this week`\n• New blog: 'FP&A for PE Portfolio Companies' — direction-of-travel into PE vertical.\n• Not our primary ICP — informational only." }
      },
      { "type": "divider" },
      {
        "type": "section",
        "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*🟢 LOW — Anaplan, Vena*\n_No significant signals this week._" }
      },
      { "type": "divider" },
      {
        "type": "section",
        "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": ":warning: *Data quality warnings*\n• ⚠️ Drivetrain pricing page returned 404 — competitor data unavailable this week. Will retry next run." }
      },
      { "type": "divider" },
      {
        "type": "section",
        "text": { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "*🎯 Recommended actions*\n• AEs in active Pigment evals: brief on the new Starter tier before next demo this week.\n• RevOps: log Pigment Starter pricing in the battlecard pricing intelligence section." }
      },
      { "type": "divider" },
      {
        "type": "context",
        "elements": [
          { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "💬 Ask anytime: `/intel <competitor> <timeframe>`  —  e.g. `/intel Pigment last 30 days`" },
          { "type": "mrkdwn", "text": "Data confidence overall: *87%* ✅  ·  Cost this run: *$0.062*  ·  <https://cloud.langfuse.com/project/abc/traces/xyz|Langfuse trace>" }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
